      "descriptions": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "JEEWMS has a missing authorization vulnerability: `/rest/tmsYwDingdanController` 运输订单 REST CRUD 缺少组织 scope. 可绕过正常页面列表的组织范围过滤，跨组织读取或篡改运输订单；`sysOrgCode` 是该业务对象的数据归属边界字段。",
          "supportingMedia": [
            {
              "base64": false,
              "type": "text/html",
              "value": "JEEWMS has a missing authorization vulnerability: `/rest/tmsYwDingdanController` 运输订单 REST CRUD 缺少组织 scope. 可绕过正常页面列表的组织范围过滤，跨组织读取或篡改运输订单；`sysOrgCode` 是该业务对象的数据归属边界字段。<p>This issue affects JEEWMS.</p>"
            }
          ]
